title: S&O Thank You Cards with Envelopes - Blank Stylish papers for Handwritten Messages -Set of 24 decor sheets and Envelopes - Assorted cute Cards with Stylish Color covers to Mix & Match
features: Express Thanks with Personality — These unique thank you cards come in 4 urbane designs. Coordinate your thank you card with a choice of 4 colored envelopes in yellow, blue, pink and sage. Craft a personalized ‘thanks’ for every recipient

Strengthen Your Relationships — Deliver a message of your gratitude and goodwill with a handwritten note. This thank you card set is suitable for your colleagues, teachers and business relations. Exhibit your attention to detail and stand out from the crowd

Two-In-One Set — No more boring white envelopes. This thank you card pack of 24 introduces eye-catching palettes of color from the moment they receive your thanks. These blank thank you cards with envelopes keep your stationery drawer fully-stocked for important events

The Power of Handwritten Notes — A handwritten thank you note goes the extra mile to show your appreciation. Flaunt your penmanship and leave your one-of-a-kind signature. Friends and loved ones will remember the birthdays and milestones you shared

Made with Sturdy Material — These card stock thank you cards are designed with a smooth, glossy exterior. The interior surface is matte for easy writing with no ink bleed. These sturdy cards are 300gsm and the envelopes are 120gsm
description: Product Description 2-in-1 Appreciation Set No need to search for an envelope to seal your thank you card. This set includes cards and color-coordinating envelopes. Reliable Paper for Heartfelt Thanks These cards are made of sturdy 300gsm cardstock with a matte interior, perfect for your handwritten note. Bright Colors & Fun Designs Mix and match your thank you cards in 6 vibrant designs with 3 options of colorful envelopes. Keep Your Stationery Stocked Special events can sneak up on a busy person like yourself. With this pack of thank you cards and envelopes, you'll have a set on hand when you need it. Something Special for Everyone No one likes to receive the same card that everyone else did. Send a different card design to every person with this variety pack, showing them they’re important. Stay Connected over the Years Communicate your love to the ones who matter most through a hand-written note. This simple gesture goes a long way. Show Appreciation to Those Who Helped You didn’t get to where you are all on your own. Acknowledge your teachers and mentors with a personal note to mark the milestones. A Card Is the Final Step Your perfectly wrapped ‘thank you’ present needs the finishing touch. A handwritten note is the perfect icing on the cake.
